        <div type="bibliography">
           <p>Essentially the same decipherment was published by F. D K. Bosch on three occasions, the first (<bibl><ptr target="bib:TBG64_1924"/><citedRange unit="page">334</citedRange><citedRange unit="section">2</citedRange></bibl>) and the second (<bibl><ptr target="bib:Bosch1924_01"/></bibl>) both marred by some typographical errors. The edition of reference is the third, that was included further on in <bibl><ptr target="bib:TBG64_1924"/><citedRange unit="page">657</citedRange><citedRange unit="item">5824</citedRange></bibl>. Re-edited here by Arlo Griffiths from photographs, revealing a part of the inscribed part of the artefact to have been lost since it was read by Bosch.</p>
